Dialogue: 0.0:00:13.23.0:00:15.23.Default..0.0.0..you can find me on  and pless support me\Nhttps://www.youtube.com/@titoGamersHaven
Dialogue: 0.0:00:15.25.0:00:17.52.Default..0.0.0..Don't tell her. though. that I said\Nanything to you.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:20.12.0:00:22.54.Default..0.0.0..You know. Rick. I don't give 7-Eleven\Nenough credit.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:22.96.0:00:24.52.Default..0.0.0..You see what those ones look like in Asia?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:24.54.0:00:26.14.Default..0.0.0..Like. like little grocery stores?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:26.50.0:00:26.86.Default..0.0.0..Porty!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:27.46.0:00:28.46.Default..0.0.0..What's that. pal?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:28.66.0:00:30.84.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. the new pool's pretty great.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:32.08.0:00:33.08.Default..0.0.0..Who are you texting?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:33.22.0:00:33.62.Default..0.0.0..Nobody.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:34.22.0:00:34.66.Default..0.0.0..Nobody?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:34.88.0:00:35.88.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. nobody.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:36.18.0:00:37.30.Default..0.0.0..Okay. fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:37.73.0:00:38.80.Default..0.0.0..Kind of a weird response.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:39.00.0:00:39.52.Default..0.0.0..Isn't that weird?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:39.72.0:00:40.72.Default..0.0.0..Privacy is a thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:40.75.0:00:42.48.Default..0.0.0..Says the guy who puts cameras everywhere.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:43.02.0:00:43.22.Default..0.0.0..Whatever.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:43.48.0:00:44.48.Default..0.0.0..Whatcha building in here?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:44.70.0:00:45.10.Default..0.0.0..Freeze ray?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:45.40.0:00:46.40.Default..0.0.0..Kinda. actually.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:46.62.0:00:47.94.Default..0.0.0..Making a beer that chills itself.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:48.22.0:00:48.40.Default..0.0.0..Morty!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:48.96.0:00:49.68.Default..0.0.0..Why are you being weird?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:49.68.0:00:51.30.Default..0.0.0..Let go of my phone. Morty!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:52.70.0:00:54.32.Default..0.0.0..Are you texting?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:54.62.0:00:55.62.Default..0.0.0..Nobody!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:56.90.0:00:58.30.Default..0.0.0..God. son of a... Come on!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:59.64.0:01:00.64.Default..0.0.0..What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:00.78.0:01:01.58.Default..0.0.0..It's fine!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:01.70.0:01:02.50.Default..0.0.0..The fuck?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:02.66.0:01:03.14.Default..0.0.0..It's fine?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:03.30.0:01:04.30.Default..0.0.0..It's fine!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:36.74.0:01:38.40.Default..0.0.0..You're texting with that guy?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:38.48.0:01:39.48.Default..0.0.0..It's stupid. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:39.64.0:01:40.76.Default..0.0.0..Seriously. it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:40.98.0:01:42.24.Default..0.0.0..Evil Morty's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:42.56.0:01:43.42.Default..0.0.0..And evil!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:43.56.0:01:44.04.Default..0.0.0..Exactly.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:44.28.0:01:47.58.Default..0.0.0..Which is why sometimes he reaches out and\Nthreatens to erase our family.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:47.76.0:01:49.88.Default..0.0.0..Unless I... help him with stuff.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:50.24.0:01:51.54.Default..0.0.0..You work for that guy?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:51.68.0:01:53.76.Default..0.0.0..He's like a Q that makes me do things for\Nhim.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:53.96.0:01:54.96.Default..0.0.0..You know Q. Morty?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:55.20.0:01:56.20.Default..0.0.0..From Star Trek?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:56.36.0:02:00.60.Default..0.0.0..Okay. so imagine a cosmic gay guy obsessed\Nwith chess.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:03.86.0:02:04.94.Default..0.0.0..You gonna pick that up?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:05.00.0:02:05.84.Default..0.0.0..You gonna make this weird?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:05.88.0:02:07.50.Default..0.0.0..I'm not allowed to be concerned!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:07.50.0:02:08.90.Default..0.0.0..You sound insane right now.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:09.18.0:02:10.18.Default..0.0.0..Hello?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:10.26.0:02:11.26.Default..0.0.0..Shit.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:11.46.0:02:11.72.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:11.90.0:02:13.26.Default..0.0.0..You don't answer my calls now?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:13.76.0:02:14.76.Default..0.0.0..Hi. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:15.20.0:02:16.40.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. feelings mutual.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:17.31.0:02:19.50.Default..0.0.0..Rick. I'm not interrupting something.\Nam I?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:19.60.0:02:24.36.Default..0.0.0..I was just catching Morty here up on\Nour... off-screen exploits.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:24.66.0:02:26.84.Default..0.0.0..You two don't share everything as a\Ncouple?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:26.96.0:02:28.30.Default..0.0.0..You know I hate you. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:28.42.0:02:28.80.Default..0.0.0..I do.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:29.12.0:02:30.72.Default..0.0.0..It's why I try to just tax...
Dialogue: 0.0:02:31.92.0:02:32.92.Default..0.0.0..Let's go.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:35.35.0:02:36.35.Default..0.0.0..What the heck?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:36.98.0:02:38.34.Default..0.0.0..Morty. you wanna come on this one?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:38.49.0:02:40.16.Default..0.0.0..At your own risk. obviously.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:40.40.0:02:41.02.Default..0.0.0..You know what?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:41.10.0:02:42.18.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. I will.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:42.40.0:02:42.66.Default..0.0.0..Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:43.02.0:02:44.02.Default..0.0.0..Cool.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:46.66.0:02:48.36.Default..0.0.0..I think we can take him.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:48.68.0:02:48.88.Default..0.0.0..We?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:49.36.0:02:50.36.Default..0.0.0..Fuck you. I'm helpful.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:50.54.0:02:51.78.Default..0.0.0..You guys scheming over there?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:52.00.0:02:52.22.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:52.22.0:02:52.22.Default..0.0.0..Yes?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:52.84.0:02:53.28.Default..0.0.0..Right.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:53.70.0:02:54.86.Default..0.0.0..Morty. you haven't seen this.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:56.48.0:02:57.82.Default..0.0.0..Anything happens to me?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:58.32.0:02:58.60.Default..0.0.0..Gone.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:59.04.0:02:59.40.Default..0.0.0..Forever.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:59.72.0:03:00.96.Default..0.0.0..Across all infinity.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:04.12.0:03:05.84.Default..0.0.0..Dude. they just sit there?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:06.12.0:03:06.40.Default..0.0.0..Always?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:06.76.0:03:08.71.Default..0.0.0..They're from an ideal\Nhostage dimension where
Dialogue: 0.0:03:08.71.0:03:10.90.Default..0.0.0..everyone's super trusting\Nand never has to shit.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:11.26.0:03:12.36.Default..0.0.0..There's no Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:12.62.0:03:14.46.Default..0.0.0..If he erases you. he erases himself.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:14.72.0:03:15.72.Default..0.0.0..Can we move this along?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:16.88.0:03:18.50.Default..0.0.0..There's a guy eating the multiverse.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:18.94.0:03:20.84.Default..0.0.0..There's always a guy eating the\Nmultiverse.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:21.08.0:03:22.42.Default..0.0.0..His name is Frumble Wormple.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:22.68.0:03:23.30.Default..0.0.0..No. it's not.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:23.44.0:03:23.86.Default..0.0.0..It's not.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:24.07.0:03:25.74.Default..0.0.0..It calls itself the Collective.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:26.08.0:03:29.70.Default..0.0.0..At some point it'll reach the central\Nfinite curve. then it'll be our problem.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:29.88.0:03:30.94.Default..0.0.0..More exposition than I expected.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:30.94.0:03:32.64.Default..0.0.0..He does this to torture me.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:32.86.0:03:33.44.Default..0.0.0..No portals.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:33.64.0:03:36.52.Default..0.0.0..This thing absorbs our stuff and learns to\Nmake its own and we're fucked.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:36.70.0:03:37.70.Default..0.0.0..You're driving.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:42.09.0:03:45.49.Default..0.0.0..Do you guys usually talk. or is it\Ndifferent because I'm here?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:45.65.0:03:45.83.Default..0.0.0..Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:45.93.0:03:46.67.Default..0.0.0..We usually talk.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:46.83.0:03:48.43.Default..0.0.0..It's boring physics stuff. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:48.67.0:03:52.37.Default..0.0.0..And you two defend the central finite\Ncurve together?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:52.65.0:03:54.55.Default..0.0.0..Since when do you care about anything?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:54.67.0:03:55.11.Default..0.0.0..I don't.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:55.27.0:03:56.43.Default..0.0.0..That's why I make him do it.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:56.59.0:03:57.83.Default..0.0.0..Thank dick we're here.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:58.61.0:04:22.17.Default..0.0.0..Oh. it sees us.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:27.38.0:04:28.38.Default..0.0.0..Get in the suit.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:28.44.0:04:28.64.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:28.96.0:04:30.66.Default..0.0.0..Morty. this is multiversal galactic shit.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:30.70.0:04:32.36.Default..0.0.0..I have to focus a little harder than\Nusual.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:32.38.0:04:32.94.Default..0.0.0..Get in the suit.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:33.10.0:04:34.18.Default..0.0.0..Make him wear the suit.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:34.22.0:04:35.54.Default..0.0.0..Evil Morty doesn't need the suit.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:37.30.0:04:38.82.Default..0.0.0..Morty. get in the suit or go home.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:40.06.0:04:42.02.Default..0.0.0..Oh. it disappears.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:42.18.0:04:42.74.Default..0.0.0..That's nifty.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:43.06.0:04:44.16.Default..0.0.0..What's that. nanomesh?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:44.26.0:04:44.90.Default..0.0.0..How's he breathing?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:45.04.0:04:46.44.Default..0.0.0..It recycles the oxygen internally.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:46.66.0:04:47.30.Default..0.0.0..Can he piss in there?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:47.46.0:04:48.58.Default..0.0.0..He can piss in there.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:48.74.0:04:49.74.Default..0.0.0..I won't need to.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:03.52.0:05:05.18.Default..0.0.0..Okay. sample container's done.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:05.34.0:05:06.42.Default..0.0.0..Should be absorption proof.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:06.58.0:05:07.34.Default..0.0.0..Huh. pretty small.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:07.56.0:05:07.76.Default..0.0.0..Nice.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:08.00.0:05:08.62.Default..0.0.0..Good stuff. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:08.80.0:05:09.28.Default..0.0.0..Very helpful.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:09.60.0:05:10.96.Default..0.0.0..Load your fucking thing in.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:17.31.0:05:18.31.Default..0.0.0..All set.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:18.45.0:05:19.45.Default..0.0.0..Let's wrap this up.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:24.12.0:05:27.80.Default..0.0.0..You are tremendous to be attempting this.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:28.06.0:05:30.78.Default..0.0.0..It will be an honor to absorb you.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:33.98.0:05:35.32.Default..0.0.0..Don't let it touch you.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:40.34.0:05:42.66.Default..0.0.0..Car. clear out.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:42.74.0:05:43.74.Default..0.0.0..Way ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:54.26.0:05:56.56.Default..0.0.0..You can't outrun me.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:56.92.0:05:58.00.Default..0.0.0..You'll be me.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:34.43.0:06:53.05.Default..0.0.0..Oh. I get it.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:03.83.0:07:06.51.Default..0.0.0..Plant these charges.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:12.69.0:07:18.19.Default..0.0.0..We have absorbed countless technologies.\NRick Sanchez.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:18.21.0:07:19.79.Default..0.0.0..One of them will be your equal.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:20.13.0:07:21.13.Default..0.0.0..Nice of you to explain.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:21.27.0:07:23.67.Default..0.0.0..The more you understand\Nof the collective. the
Dialogue: 0.0:07:23.67.0:07:26.89.Default..0.0.0..easier you will be for\Nthe collective to absorb.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:27.13.0:07:28.13.Default..0.0.0..Lucky me.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:32.58.0:07:37.43.Default..0.0.0..This is me. but it is coating something\Nthat is not me.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:38.43.0:07:40.65.Default..0.0.0..We are the collective.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:41.17.0:07:42.83.Default..0.0.0..I am the collective.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:43.87.0:07:50.45.Default..0.0.0..I did not say or think those things.\Nand I don't think I sound like that.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:52.41.0:07:53.79.Default..0.0.0..What are these?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:54.25.0:07:57.89.Default..0.0.0..Uh. definitely not charges of some kind.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:58.03.0:08:00.25.Default..0.0.0..I think that's exactly what they are.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:00.43.0:08:02.81.Default..0.0.0..I will absorb them.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:04.27.0:08:05.27.Default..0.0.0..Shit.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:05.73.0:08:10.69.Default..0.0.0..I am the Threads of Time. bound and\Nperfected.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:11.11.0:08:14.15.Default..0.0.0..And your time is up.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:19.97.0:08:20.97.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:23.95.0:08:25.33.Default..0.0.0..I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:26.05.0:08:27.57.Default..0.0.0..I am the collective.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:28.13.0:08:29.63.Default..0.0.0..I absorb all.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:30.11.0:08:32.63.Default..0.0.0..Right. and you just absorbed a compression\Nalgorithm.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:33.31.0:08:33.57.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:33.77.0:08:35.67.Default..0.0.0..Now you'll absorb yourself forever.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:39.87.0:08:40.87.Default..0.0.0..Impossible!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:41.35.0:08:42.75.Default..0.0.0..I am the collective!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:45.55.0:08:47.35.Default..0.0.0..I am the collective!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:51.85.0:08:52.97.Default..0.0.0..Way to get captured.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:53.35.0:08:54.57.Default..0.0.0..Obviously not my fault.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:54.87.0:08:56.23.Default..0.0.0..You really fucked me there. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:56.83.0:08:59.09.Default..0.0.0..Definitely not charges of some kind.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:59.19.0:09:00.21.Default..0.0.0..It was stressful. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:00.51.0:09:01.63.Default..0.0.0..That was... cheese.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:01.93.0:09:03.81.Default..0.0.0..Although. getting captured kind of worked\Nout.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:03.93.0:09:04.79.Default..0.0.0..I didn't mind it.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:04.79.0:09:05.89.Default..0.0.0..I like talking to that guy.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:06.03.0:09:07.91.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. way better than the dude from last\Nweek.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:08.53.0:09:12.03.Default..0.0.0..So you guys do stuff like that together a\Nlot?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:13.27.0:09:14.27.Default..0.0.0..Only sometimes.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:14.81.0:09:15.81.Default..0.0.0..Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:15.93.0:09:16.93.Default..0.0.0..Should we hit a diner?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:17.01.0:09:18.01.Default..0.0.0..Is that crazy?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:18.05.0:09:18.67.Default..0.0.0..Get some waffles?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:19.03.0:09:19.25.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:19.53.0:09:19.85.Default..0.0.0..No!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:20.43.0:09:22.07.Default..0.0.0..Rick. tell Morty we're getting waffles.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:29.72.0:09:30.72.Default..0.0.0..Something to drink.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:31.13.0:09:33.99.Default..0.0.0..One. uh. two milkshakes. actually.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:34.45.0:09:35.51.Default..0.0.0..Coffee with vodka in it.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:35.57.0:09:36.57.Default..0.0.0..Amen.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:36.91.0:09:37.91.Default..0.0.0..You have fun. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:38.33.0:09:39.81.Default..0.0.0..Today was actually a pretty good one.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:39.99.0:09:41.39.Default..0.0.0..And you only threw us off a little.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:41.47.0:09:42.25.Default..0.0.0..My apologies.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:42.25.0:09:43.25.Default..0.0.0..All good.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:43.39.0:09:45.25.Default..0.0.0..Me and Rick just have a... rhythm.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:45.53.0:09:47.01.Default..0.0.0..It's a fiercely unsteady truce.\NMorty.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:47.31.0:09:49.27.Default..0.0.0..Either of us could backstab the other at\Nany time.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:49.29.0:09:50.79.Default..0.0.0..I get why he never looped you in.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:51.11.0:09:54.91.Default..0.0.0..I mean. if I'm calling this guy.\Nhe must be this tall to ride. you know?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:55.19.0:09:55.75.Default..0.0.0..I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:56.05.0:09:57.33.Default..0.0.0..Don't let him rile you up. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:57.35.0:09:58.35.Default..0.0.0..It's all dumb.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:58.57.0:10:01.83.Default..0.0.0..Mostly just levitating with power and\Nscreaming as our eyes glow.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:01.99.0:10:03.65.Default..0.0.0..Sometimes we do a huge beam together.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:03.81.0:10:04.65.Default..0.0.0..What even are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:04.81.0:10:05.21.Default..0.0.0..Jesus.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:05.51.0:10:07.21.Default..0.0.0..May I go to the bathroom. please?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:07.55.0:10:09.25.Default..0.0.0..I gotta give these waffles some runway.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:09.41.0:10:10.45.Default..0.0.0..What do I look like?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:10.65.0:10:11.65.Default..0.0.0..A bad guy?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:12.03.0:10:13.53.Default..0.0.0..You are... permitted.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:14.65.0:10:16.53.Default..0.0.0..He's a big softie once you get to know\Nhim. huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:16.83.0:10:19.37.Default..0.0.0..He even showed me some... time travel\Nstuff.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:19.69.0:10:21.53.Default..0.0.0..I'm gonna shove these waffles up your ass.\Npal.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:21.85.0:10:22.29.Default..0.0.0..Heavens.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:22.31.0:10:23.43.Default..0.0.0..What the fuck are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:23.45.0:10:24.65.Default..0.0.0..You gonna replace me?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:24.81.0:10:26.19.Default..0.0.0..I'm not sure what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:26.21.0:10:26.83.Default..0.0.0..Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:27.11.0:10:27.55.Default..0.0.0..Homewrecker.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:27.61.0:10:28.61.Default..0.0.0..You see this?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:28.89.0:10:31.49.Default..0.0.0..All this messy... whatever this is?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:31.99.0:10:32.99.Default..0.0.0..It's weakness.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:33.03.0:10:33.55.Default..0.0.0..Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:33.79.0:10:34.79.Default..0.0.0..You know what?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:34.95.0:10:36.47.Default..0.0.0..Maybe I will steal your grandpa.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:36.73.0:10:38.17.Default..0.0.0..But not because I love him.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:38.57.0:10:39.57.Default..0.0.0..Because you do.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:39.65.0:10:40.65.Default..0.0.0..Here we go.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:40.95.0:10:43.23.Default..0.0.0..Two milkshakes for the two kinds of\NMortys.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:43.49.0:10:44.89.Default..0.0.0..The one who does whatever he wants.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:45.15.0:10:46.99.Default..0.0.0..And the one who sucks my grandpa's dick.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:47.71.0:10:48.19.Default..0.0.0..You know what?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:48.60.0:10:49.81.Default..0.0.0..I'll drink both milkshakes.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:49.97.0:10:52.19.Default..0.0.0..This dick is shit so big it changed my\Nbrain chemistry.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:52.63.0:10:53.37.Default..0.0.0..What are we doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:53.63.0:10:54.71.Default..0.0.0..We order those waffles yet?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:54.73.0:10:55.33.Default..0.0.0..Can we go?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:55.59.0:10:57.43.Default..0.0.0..Morty. I took such a nice shit.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:57.53.0:10:58.99.Default..0.0.0..Don't make him tug my leash again.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:59.13.0:11:00.33.Default..0.0.0..Oh. we can call it.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:00.47.0:11:01.63.Default..0.0.0..Boy. this was great. though.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:01.85.0:11:03.09.Default..0.0.0..Thanks for coming along. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:03.29.0:11:05.79.Default..0.0.0..Rick. we gotta do this after missions more\Noften.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:05.87.0:11:06.87.Default..0.0.0..Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:07.41.0:11:08.49.Default..0.0.0..This one's on me.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:08.94.0:11:11.29.Default..0.0.0..And. uh. till next time. Gramps.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:12.81.0:11:13.69.Default..0.0.0..I winked.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:13.77.0:11:15.47.Default..0.0.0..Maybe you couldn't tell because of the\Neyepatch.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:15.49.0:11:16.13.Default..0.0.0..We could tell.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:16.44.0:11:17.44.Default..0.0.0..Blackmailing prick.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:44.01.0:11:44.53.Default..0.0.0..Motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:44.63.0:11:45.63.Default..0.0.0..Yeah!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:47.47.0:11:51.15.Default..0.0.0..I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:51.33.0:11:55.19.Default..0.0.0..I put the blueprints for that dumb fucking\NOmega device in the Omega device. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:55.47.0:11:57.63.Default..0.0.0..It even wiped from every possible reality.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:57.73.0:11:59.89.Default..0.0.0..You mean... Yes. you\Npossessive fucking nerd.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:59.89.0:12:02.23.Default..0.0.0..We're free of that hack bullshit once and\Nfor all.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:02.59.0:12:03.77.Default..0.0.0..Uh-oh. sweet bliss.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:04.05.0:12:05.93.Default..0.0.0..I'm already forgetting what we're talking\Nabout.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:06.95.0:12:08.71.Default..0.0.0..God. he brought you along to flex.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:09.03.0:12:10.03.Default..0.0.0..He showed you his lair.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:10.07.0:12:11.35.Default..0.0.0..That overconfident little bitch.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:11.43.0:12:12.15.Default..0.0.0..Predictable bitch!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:12.31.0:12:14.43.Default..0.0.0..That's what happens when you get too used\Nto winning. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:14.45.0:12:16.15.Default..0.0.0..You start sucking your own dick.\NMorty.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:21.63.0:12:23.15.Default..0.0.0..He's gonna be coming for us. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:23.29.0:12:25.11.Default..0.0.0..He's coming. and he's gonna be pissed.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:25.35.0:12:27.41.Default..0.0.0..He doesn't have the luxury of subtlety\Nanymore.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:27.71.0:12:28.71.Default..0.0.0..That smug dick.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:34.98.0:12:36.88.Default..0.0.0..Don't wanna murder the shit out of me.\NMorty.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:37.14.0:12:38.58.Default..0.0.0..That's why I built this place.\NMorty.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:38.82.0:12:40.78.Default..0.0.0..This whole dimension is a bunker.\NMorty.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:41.10.0:12:41.90.Default..0.0.0..Oh. man.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:42.00.0:12:43.54.Default..0.0.0..We live in the bunker now. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:43.68.0:12:45.16.Default..0.0.0..We might be here forever. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:45.62.0:12:46.62.Default..0.0.0..Bunker dimension!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:47.88.0:12:50.16.Default..0.0.0..So. Evil Morty thinks he's my nemesis.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:50.32.0:12:51.32.Default..0.0.0..Mostly just sucks.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:51.40.0:12:52.40.Default..0.0.0..But he is deadly.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:52.62.0:12:53.10.Default..0.0.0..Swallow this.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:53.24.0:12:55.30.Default..0.0.0..It's a kind of body armor goo so you can\Ntake some hits.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:55.32.0:12:55.98.Default..0.0.0..But only some.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:56.18.0:12:57.42.Default..0.0.0..I'm not made of body armor goo.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:57.46.0:12:58.46.Default..0.0.0..What about Space Beth?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:58.62.0:13:00.12.Default..0.0.0..Space Beth is mean to me sometimes.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:00.26.0:13:02.38.Default..0.0.0..There's an evil version of Morty?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:02.38.0:13:03.66.Default..0.0.0..Yes. Jerry. obviously.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:03.86.0:13:04.22.Default..0.0.0..Keep up.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:04.32.0:13:06.48.Default..0.0.0..He's crafty. he's evil. he's a pussy-ass\Nbitch.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:06.66.0:13:10.32.Default..0.0.0..He doesn't think I know this. but his\Nstupid Akira palm laser has a cool down.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:10.64.0:13:12.82.Default..0.0.0..You get 20 seconds after firing it to\Ntackle him.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:12.92.0:13:14.46.Default..0.0.0..If he corners you. yell a slur.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:14.62.0:13:15.46.Default..0.0.0..A bad slur.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:15.58.0:13:15.88.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:16.04.0:13:17.10.Default..0.0.0..That reaction exactly.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:17.30.0:13:19.10.Default..0.0.0..The worse the slur. the more time it buys\Nyou.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:19.30.0:13:20.90.Default..0.0.0..Jerry. pretend to shit your pants in fear.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:20.92.0:13:22.04.Default..0.0.0..I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:22.16.0:13:23.60.Default..0.0.0..So we just live here now?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:23.62.0:13:24.18.Default..0.0.0..On high alert.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:24.30.0:13:27.12.Default..0.0.0..But also. open your heart to the joys of\Nthe bunker dimension.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:27.42.0:13:30.30.Default..0.0.0..There's normal plumbing. and your friends\Nand neighbors all have combat training.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:30.32.0:13:31.36.Default..0.0.0..Like Bunker Gene here.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:32.10.0:13:32.50.Default..0.0.0..Oorah.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:32.96.0:13:33.96.Default..0.0.0..At ease. PG.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:34.00.0:13:35.00.Default..0.0.0..Now. ballistics.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:35.20.0:13:36.88.Default..0.0.0..Evil Morty does have a force field.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:37.16.0:13:37.76.Default..0.0.0..It's annoying.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:38.00.0:13:40.06.Default..0.0.0..Is Bunker Gene from this dimension?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:40.36.0:13:41.62.Default..0.0.0..Or do you think we could have brought him\Nhere?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:41.64.0:13:42.96.Default..0.0.0..Seems like he used to be a marine.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:42.98.0:13:43.52.Default..0.0.0..No whispering.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:43.86.0:13:45.74.Default..0.0.0..Whispering's the first step to turning on\Neach other.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:45.76.0:13:46.78.Default..0.0.0..He might go for that too.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:47.02.0:13:48.02.Default..0.0.0..Classic bunker maneuver.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:48.12.0:13:50.04.Default..0.0.0..Just let us stew in here until we go\Ninsane.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:50.18.0:13:52.68.Default..0.0.0..So we can't go insane. even if we live\Nhere forever.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:53.16.0:13:54.16.Default..0.0.0..More questions?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:54.64.0:13:55.64.Default..0.0.0..No further questions.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:00.33.0:14:02.53.Default..0.0.0..Do you wish I was smarter?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:02.79.0:14:04.21.Default..0.0.0..Oh. Morty. have some dignity.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:04.41.0:14:06.39.Default..0.0.0..I don't know. maybe it was all an act.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:06.86.0:14:11.03.Default..0.0.0..But he's powerful and confident.\Nand you guys had real chemistry.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:11.59.0:14:13.23.Default..0.0.0..I can't even do chemistry homework.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:13.35.0:14:15.39.Default..0.0.0..He wears a villain accessory. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:15.55.0:14:16.87.Default..0.0.0..We are closing the book on this.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:17.05.0:14:18.05.Default..0.0.0..Evil Morty sucks.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:18.39.0:14:18.91.Default..0.0.0..You promise?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:19.33.0:14:19.99.Default..0.0.0..I promise.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:20.35.0:14:20.59.Default..0.0.0..Phew.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:21.17.0:14:23.09.Default..0.0.0..And you're sure he can't break in?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:23.23.0:14:23.87.Default..0.0.0..It's unlikely.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:24.17.0:14:25.63.Default..0.0.0..Unless he's canonically\Nmastered the tech needed
Dialogue: 0.0:14:25.63.0:14:27.17.Default..0.0.0..to board through\Ndimensional infrastructure.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:27.33.0:14:29.17.Default..0.0.0..I don't know. I don't keep track of that\Nstuff.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:30.29.0:14:35.41.Default..0.0.0..I'm happy you don't like him more than me.\NRick.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:35.41.0:14:37.91.Default..0.0.0..I think this one might be for keepsies.\NMorty.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:38.27.0:14:38.83.Default..0.0.0..Shoot to kill.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:39.01.0:14:40.01.Default..0.0.0..Roger that.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:55.12.0:14:56.87.Default..0.0.0..Did it work. sir?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:57.89.0:14:58.89.Default..0.0.0..It worked.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:00.21.0:15:01.21.Default..0.0.0..You
Dialogue: 0.0:15:15.62.0:15:17.60.Default..0.0.0..built a bunker dimension just for me.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:17.74.0:15:18.62.Default..0.0.0..I don't have to lie here.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:18.74.0:15:20.16.Default..0.0.0..I built it for a bunch of reasons.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:20.28.0:15:21.54.Default..0.0.0..You're not special. pal.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:21.60.0:15:22.60.Default..0.0.0..I don't need to be.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:26.20.0:15:28.14.Default..0.0.0..You're gonna watch me kill him.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:28.26.0:15:30.26.Default..0.0.0..Oh man. you sound as pressed as Morty was.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:30.26.0:15:31.60.Default..0.0.0..You do have a lot in common.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:35.80.0:15:36.40.Default..0.0.0..That's cute.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:36.60.0:15:37.84.Default..0.0.0..How many of those you got left?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:38.30.0:15:39.30.Default..0.0.0..Like. two?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:39.62.0:15:40.62.Default..0.0.0..Is it two?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:41.08.0:15:42.08.Default..0.0.0..Three?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:42.28.0:17:33.47.Default..0.0.0..Oh. fuck you!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:33.55.0:17:34.63.Default..0.0.0..You're really gonna do this?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:34.65.0:17:36.61.Default..0.0.0..You're really gonna try to make him shoot\Nme?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:36.75.0:17:37.59.Default..0.0.0..That's your trick?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:37.73.0:17:40.47.Default..0.0.0..Just say your whole plan out loud so he\Ndoesn't suspect you?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:41.53.0:17:42.53.Default..0.0.0..Shit.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:57.48.0:17:59.01.Default..0.0.0..I really do hate you guys.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:59.43.0:18:00.07.Default..0.0.0..No. you don't.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:00.33.0:18:02.53.Default..0.0.0..That's the real reason you need to kill us\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:02.75.0:18:05.03.Default..0.0.0..Because for Rick. making me jealous was an\Nact.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:05.37.0:18:06.37.Default..0.0.0..But for you?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:06.87.0:18:08.23.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. run. bitch.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:08.41.0:18:10.93.Default..0.0.0..You leaned in hard because you thought it\Nwas real.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:11.45.0:18:11.79.Default..0.0.0..Damn. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:12.11.0:18:13.11.Default..0.0.0..I saw what I saw. Rick.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:13.19.0:18:15.25.Default..0.0.0..He's got a big ol' crush on you.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:15.33.0:18:16.41.Default..0.0.0..I'd like to deny it. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:16.51.0:18:17.89.Default..0.0.0..But I'm pretty irresistible.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:21.17.0:18:26.39.Default..0.0.0..Well. maybe it's us who need to run.\Nbitch.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:32.17.0:18:32.65.Default..0.0.0..Jerry!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:33.01.0:18:34.01.Default..0.0.0..Not helping. Dad!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:36.39.0:18:37.39.Default..0.0.0..Twenty seconds!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:37.51.0:18:38.51.Default..0.0.0..Jump him!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:39.05.0:18:41.27.Default..0.0.0..Get your little iPad. you piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:50.23.0:18:51.23.Default..0.0.0..You like that?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:51.71.0:18:53.25.Default..0.0.0..That little time device you showed me?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:53.57.0:18:54.57.Default..0.0.0..I made one too.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:54.89.0:18:55.99.Default..0.0.0..Just like the portal gun.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:56.53.0:18:58.79.Default..0.0.0..Always struck me as odd that Rick's don't\Ndo time travel.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:59.21.0:19:01.15.Default..0.0.0..I get that it's messy. but so are you.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:01.95.0:19:04.41.Default..0.0.0..Anyways. good thing I'm not a Rick.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:06.27.0:19:07.41.Default..0.0.0..Hey. that's what I can see!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:07.61.0:19:11.37.Default..0.0.0..You're surrounded for a thousand years in\Nany direction. you sick fuck!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:39.88.0:19:40.88.Default..0.0.0..Thanks for the tip-off.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:41.10.0:19:42.74.Default..0.0.0..A lot of people freezing time these days.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:42.77.0:19:44.88.Default..0.0.0..Just a concerned citizen officer.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:45.10.0:19:47.18.Default..0.0.0..This societal breakdown is what it is.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:47.40.0:19:49.74.Default..0.0.0..Nobody pulling over for ambulances no more\Nneither.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:49.98.0:19:51.14.Default..0.0.0..Alright. get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:51.32.0:19:53.02.Default..0.0.0..I want this kid processed yesterday.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:53.80.0:19:54.82.Default..0.0.0..Hey. wait up!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:56.92.0:19:57.92.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:59.06.0:20:00.06.Default..0.0.0..Oh shit!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:01.12.0:20:03.64.Default..0.0.0..You touch me with that hand again and I'll\Nfucking cube it. pal.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:03.94.0:20:04.94.Default..0.0.0..You're nothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:04.98.0:20:06.48.Default..0.0.0..You're less than nothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:07.34.0:20:08.34.Default..0.0.0..Morty's right.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:08.44.0:20:09.44.Default..0.0.0..You do have a crush.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:09.72.0:20:11.00.Default..0.0.0..You needed the cops to win.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:11.15.0:20:12.15.Default..0.0.0..Ugh. scoreboard.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:14.02.0:20:15.34.Default..0.0.0..Sorry. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:15.50.0:20:15.96.Default..0.0.0..You made it weird.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:16.20.0:20:17.20.Default..0.0.0..We were never a thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:17.56.0:20:17.96.Default..0.0.0..Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:18.18.0:20:20.08.Default..0.0.0..Enjoy prison. fucker!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:24.72.0:20:25.72.Default..0.0.0..Season nine. baby.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:27.74.0:20:29.94.Default..0.0.0..Only an indefinite number more.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:30.48.0:20:32.28.Default..0.0.0..Sure glad we didn't have to use those\Nslurs.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:32.56.0:20:33.56.Default..0.0.0..Oh my god. same.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:33.60.0:20:34.60.Default..0.0.0..You had one ready?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:34.76.0:20:36.02.Default..0.0.0..No. don't act like you didn't.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:36.42.0:20:37.92.Default..0.0.0..Let's all say them at the same time.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:38.24.0:20:39.98.Default..0.0.0..Three. two. one.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:40.66.0:20:41.66.Default..0.0.0..Ew!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:41.70.0:20:42.04.Default..0.0.0..Ew!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:42.54.0:20:43.54.Default..0.0.0..Wow!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:43.76.0:20:45.68.Default..0.0.0..Evil Morty off the board for good.\Nhuh?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:45.96.0:20:47.28.Default..0.0.0..What are you gonna do now. Rick?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:47.52.0:20:48.86.Default..0.0.0..Nothing but green. you know?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:49.15.0:20:51.02.Default..0.0.0..Green grass in front of us. baby.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:51.08.0:20:52.08.Default..0.0.0..I need a vacation.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:52.50.0:20:52.70.Default..0.0.0..Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:53.44.0:20:54.44.Default..0.0.0..Nice.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:56.05.0:20:57.98.Default..0.0.0..But you do like me more than him.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:58.12.0:20:59.12.Default..0.0.0..Don't be needy. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:34.61.0:21:37.45.Default..0.0.0..When are you in for. ape?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:37.45.0:21:38.53.Default..0.0.0..This is it?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:38.61.0:21:41.19.Default..0.0.0..You're not gonna put me in stasis for all\Nof time?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:41.53.0:21:43.27.Default..0.0.0..Or. I don't know. remove my consciousness?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:43.69.0:21:43.89.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:44.07.0:21:45.83.Default..0.0.0..Bro. this shit's supposed to be punitive.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:46.11.0:21:48.31.Default..0.0.0..What the hell sucks about going to sleep?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:48.75.0:21:49.75.Default..0.0.0..Nah. little man.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:49.89.0:21:51.61.Default..0.0.0..Y'all gonna be eating mush on a tray.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:51.83.0:21:54.75.Default..0.0.0..With like big aggro dudes that call you\Nfish. relentlessly.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:55.17.0:21:55.45.Default..0.0.0..Damn.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:55.63.0:21:57.25.Default..0.0.0..I mean. you can get jacked.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:57.37.0:21:59.99.Default..0.0.0..But even then. you gotta hustle for that\Nprotein.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:00.15.0:22:01.29.Default..0.0.0..You guys have prison pegs.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:01.37.0:22:02.61.Default..0.0.0..We have forever to do it.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:07.67.0:22:09.13.Default..0.0.0..Did you get any of that?
